      <p class="bm-hero__lead">A compact dynamic-planar hybrid tuned for a modern and lively sound signature. The miniature planar magnetic tweeter delivers crystal-clear vocal and treble detail, while the 10mm graphene dynamic driver supplies natural, robust sub-bass. Physical crossover, 3D-printed acoustic chamber, and daily-ready universal fit.</p>
