    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bm-section bm-story">
    <div class="bm-wrap bm-story__grid">
      <div>
        <p class="bm-kicker">Design Story</p>
        <h2>A dynamic-planar hybrid with AAW digital acoustic design.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="bm-prose">
        <p>The Z02 showcases an innovative dynamic-planar hybrid multi-driver system, meticulously tuned for a modern and lively sound signature. It delivers a natural and robust sub-bass response, unmatched by traditional all-balanced armature setups, while its miniature planar magnetic tweeter keeps vocal and treble detail clean, extended, and smooth.</p>
        <p>The planar magnetic tweeter is embedded deep into the Z02's 3D-printed shell. Its dedicated cavity design eliminates sound pressure decay and unwanted resonance common to traditional tubed balanced armature designs. The thin diaphragm responds quickly to signal changes, giving Z02 accurate dynamics, low distortion, and a consistent soundstage.</p>
        <p>With a wholly digitized design process, Z02 employs AAW third-generation digital enclosure and acoustic chamber design. Driver and nozzle placements are simulated through hundreds of iterations to determine ideal phasing and response, then 3D printed to precision for production consistency.</p>
        <p>Suitable for rising artists, band performances, streaming platforms, worship events, audio engineering, and anybody who appreciates a critical listening experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bm-section bm-section--dark">
    <div class="bm-wrap bm-section-head">
      <p class="bm-kicker">Fitment Options</p>
      <h2>Designed for a stable universal seal.</h2>
      <p>Z02 ships with assorted ear tips so listeners can tune seal, comfort, bass weight, and treble energy by fit. The compact shell is shaped through AAW's digital enclosure process for ergonomic daily use.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-wrap z02-original-grid">
      <figure>
        <img src="{{ 'z02-lifestyle-wide.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="AAW Z02 universal in-ear monitors with detachable copper cable" width="2200" height="1467" loading="lazy">
        <figcaption><b>Universal fit</b><span>Compact shell, detachable cable, and tip rolling flexibility for daily listening.</span></figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure>
        <img src="{{ 'z02-detail-square.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="AAW Z02 faceplates and detachable cable close up" width="1600" height="1600" loading="lazy">
        <figcaption><b>Fit tuning</b><span>Assorted tips let the user tune seal pressure, isolation, and tonal balance.</span></figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bm-section bm-section--dark" id="z02-architecture">
    <div class="bm-wrap bm-section-head">
      <p class="bm-kicker">Acoustic Architecture</p>
      <h2>Planar speed. Graphene low end. One coherent physical crossover.</h2>
      <p>The miniature planar magnetic tweeter handles upper detail with low distortion, wide dispersion, and fast transient response. The 10mm graphene dynamic driver uses a rigid ultra-thin diaphragm and physical low-pass filtering to keep bass focused with minimal overlap. Driver placement and acoustic chambers are digitally simulated, then 3D printed for consistency.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-wrap z02-explosion-panel">
      <figure>
        <img src="{{ 'z02-driver-diagram.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="AAW Z02 driver diagram with miniature planar tweeter assembly and shell components" width="1800" height="1064" loading="lazy">
        <figcaption><b>Miniature planar magnetic tweeter assembly</b><span>Lower valve cover, magnet arrays, thin film circuit pattern, top valve cover, 2-pin socket, faceplate, and finished shell geometry.</span></figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-wrap z02-architecture-map">
      <div class="z02-architecture-map__head">
        <img class="z02-card-logo" src="{{ 'z02-logo-lockup.png' | asset_url }}" alt="AAW Z02" width="900" height="193" loading="lazy">
        <span>Z02 Driver Configuration</span>
      </div>
      <div class="z02-architecture-map__crossover">
        <span>2-Way Hybrid Crossover</span>
        <small>Physical low-pass filtering - Phase-aware placement - 3D-printed chamber</small>
      </div>
      <div class="z02-architecture-map__grid">
        <article>
          <div class="z02-driver-icon z02-driver-icon--dynamic"><span>DD</span></div>
          <span>Band 1</span>
          <h3>Graphene Dynamic</h3>
          <p>10mm graphene diaphragm driver supplies natural sub-bass and low-frequency body.</p>
          <b>1 x dynamic driver</b>
        </article>
        <article>
          <div class="z02-driver-icon z02-driver-icon--planar"><span>PM</span></div>
          <span>Band 2</span>
          <h3>Planar Tweeter</h3>
