  </section>

  <section class="bm-section bm-section--dark">
    <div class="bm-wrap bm-section-head">
      <p class="bm-kicker">Sound Signature &amp; Frequency Response</p>
      <h2>Modern, lively, and measured.</h2>
      <p>Z02 is tuned with a natural and robust sub-bass foundation, clear vocal presence, carefully managed treble extension, and a smooth fatigue-free presentation. The frequency response reflects the dynamic-planar crossover balance and AAW's 3D-printed chamber tuning.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-wrap z02-switch-grid" aria-label="Z02 sound characteristics">
      <article><span>Low</span><h3>Robust sub-bass</h3><p>The graphene dynamic driver gives Z02 a physical bass foundation that all-BA designs cannot reproduce in the same way.</p></article>
      <article><span>Mid</span><h3>Clean vocal focus</h3><p>The planar tweeter keeps vocals articulate and immediate without pushing the presentation into harshness.</p></article>
      <article><span>High</span><h3>Extended detail</h3><p>Fast planar transient response preserves treble texture, cymbal air, and micro-detail.</p></article>
      <article><span>Stage</span><h3>Stable imaging</h3><p>Digitized driver placement and chamber design help maintain coherent timing and a consistent soundstage.</p></article>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-wrap z02-benefit-grid" aria-label="Miniature planar magnetic tweeter benefits">
      <article><span>01</span><h3>Low distortion</h3><p>The evenly driven diaphragm reduces non-linear behavior and harshness in the upper range.</p></article>
      <article><span>02</span><h3>Compact size</h3><p>Miniaturized planar technology fits inside an IEM shell without giving up treble performance.</p></article>
      <article><span>03</span><h3>Fast dynamics</h3><p>The thin diaphragm responds quickly to transient sounds and dynamic changes.</p></article>
      <article><span>04</span><h3>Wide dispersion</h3><p>Uniform sound dispersion supports a more consistent soundstage across listening angles.</p></article>
    </div>
    <div class="bm-wrap z02-fr-figure">
      <figure>
        <img src="{{ 'Z02-FR_5fb85fc0-6b97-46e2-a9d5-0031f8aa6a25.jpg' | file_url }}" alt="AAW Z02 frequency response measurement graph" width="2000" height="1200" loading="lazy">
        <figcaption>Z02 frequency response measurement. Dynamic-planar hybrid tuning balances natural low-end weight with smooth vocal and treble extension.</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

